 https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em>《Back To Black》</em>首次以故事片形式讲述了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)</a>的故事，在下个月（4 月 12 日）上映之前，我们将在<em>NME</em>上独家发布三张特别电影海报。看看下面的内容。 </p><figure id="attachment_3610262" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3610262" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3610262" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_2.jpg" alt="回到黑色" width="2000" height="2961" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_2-400x592.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_2-800x1184.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_2-696x1030.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_2-1392x2061.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_2-1068x1581.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3610262" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Studiocanal </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3610263" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3610263" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3610263" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_Marisa_Abela_Insta.jpg" alt="回到黑色" width="2000" height="2961" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_Marisa_Abela_Insta.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_Marisa_Abela_Insta-400x592.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_Marisa_Abela_Insta-800x1184.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_Marisa_Abela_Insta-696x1030.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_Marisa_Abela_Insta-1392x2061.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster_Marisa_Abela_Insta-1068x1581.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3610263" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Studiocanal </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3610265" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3610265" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3610265" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster.jpg" alt="回到黑色" width="2000" height="2961" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster-400x592.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster-800x1184.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster-696x1030.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster-1392x2061.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Back_To_Black_Poster-1068x1581.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3610265" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Studiocanal</figcaption></figure><p>艾米从十几岁开始在伦敦北部长大，一直到她在 2000 年代迅速崛起并获得格莱美奖， <em>《重返黑色</em>》（4 月 12 日上映）由<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/industry"><em>行业</em></a>女演员玛丽莎·阿贝拉 (Marisa Abela) 领衔主演，并与英国电影和电视艺术学院 (BAFTA) 提名演员一起主演杰克·奥康奈尔（Jack O&#39;Connell）饰演怀恩豪斯的前夫布莱克·菲尔德-西维尔（Blake Fielder-Civil），广受好评的女演员莱斯利·曼维尔（Lesley Manville）饰演她的祖母贾尼斯·利维（Janis Levy）。埃迪·马森和朱丽叶·考恩将饰演艾米的父母米奇·怀恩豪斯和贾尼斯·怀恩豪斯。</p><p>该片由萨姆·泰勒-约翰逊执导，他曾执导过 2009 年广受好评的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>传记片《<em>无处男孩》</em>以及改编自色情小说<em>《五十度灰》</em>的大银幕。马特·格林哈尔（ <em>《无处男孩》</em> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ian-curtis">伊恩·柯蒂斯</a>传记片<em>《控制</em>》）撰写了剧本。</p><p> “我们真的很想从[艾米]的角度，通过她的眼睛来做到这一点；让我们通过她的音乐和她的话语踏上旅程，这样我们就能回到她身边。”一月份第一部预告片曝光时，泰勒-约翰逊告诉<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/back-to-black-interview-director-sam-taylor-johnson-amy-winehouse-casting-marisa-abela-blake/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《帝国》杂志</em></a>。 “而不是纪录片，后者非常注重外部视角。我想要感觉我们在她的创作过程中与她在一起。”</p><p>上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soundtrack-announced-for-new-amy-winehouse-back-to-black-movie-including-original-song-by-nick-cave-3605389">我们分享了<em>《Back To Black》</em>官方原声带的详细信息</a>，其中包括歌手本人的歌曲以及其他标志性艺术家的歌曲。其中包括 2003 年首张专辑《Frank》中的三首歌曲、《Back To Black》中的另外三首歌曲，以及启发艾米灵感的艺术家的五首歌曲：The Shangri-Las、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-holiday">Billie Holiday</a> 、Minnie Riperton、Dinah Washington 和 Sarah沃恩。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave</a> ) 与长期合作者、坏种子乐队成员沃伦·埃利斯 (Warren Ellis) 共同创作了这部电影的配乐，他还创作了一首原创曲目，名为《Song For Amy》，向怀恩豪斯致敬。</p><p>这张合辑专辑名为“Back To Black: Songss from the Original Motion Picture”，定于 5 月 17 日通过 UMR/Island Records 发行。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/back-to-black-posters-amy-winehouse-3610218">看看这些独家的《Back To Black》电影海报，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
